  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to analyze the factors influencing the medical and non-medical
      direct costs of patients treated with biotherapy during the last twelve months (infliximab or
      adalimumab), including biosimilars (infliximab biosimilars: Inflectra ™ and Remsima ™) for
      treating Crohn's desease or ulcerative colitis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
